Title: cadvisor_if: Network check for cAdvisor metrics from Prometheus
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1580973599
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

This check plugin can be used for Prometheus retrieved metrics
concerning network interface information from the cAdvisor. The
information can be grouped by pod level. In order to monitor this
information, one must configure in the Prometheus Datasource Program
ruleset.
